        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-5 col-xs-offset-2 col-sm-2 col-sm-offset-0">
            <%= image_tag @opponent_team_captain.photo, class: "img-responsive"%><br>
            <div class="text-center">
                <span><%= @opponent_team_captain.name %></span>
            </div>
        </div> <!-- end of column -->
        <div class="hidden-xs col-sm-4">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam sit amet diam id magna pharetra porta. Suspendisse tortor erat, malesuada eget vehicula ac, facilisis ut eros. Aliquam consequat sem id posuere maximus. Mauris tempus massa a leo tempus fringilla. Donec id mattis dui. Morbi id varius elit. In nec finibus turpis, id lacinia erat. Phasellus in nisl nisl.
        </div>
    </div> <!-- end of row -->

    <div class="row row-content">
        <p class="space"></p>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <%= render @first_team %>
        </div>


        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <%= render @opponent_team %>
        </div> <!-- End of column -->
	</div> <!-- End of row -->

</div> <!-- end of container -->
